imdb.plot outline: Miley, also known by her family as Momay, was the daughter of the owners of a carnival named "La Vida Funland". Her father had died from a brain tumor, causing devastation to her family. Her mother Shirley had to remain independent for the children. As Shirley manages the carnival she encountered some problems such as accidents in which one of her employees died. It was then believed that the husband of the employees went into their house, causing arson which apparently have accidentally killed the girl. The husband remained pleading not guilty for the accident. After Momay's death, Shirley's depression managed to get the better of her, as she disappears from thin air leaving Justin into the care of Hillary, Momay and Justin's aunt who had a fixation with taking over the La Vida Funland business. As Momay passed into purgatory, she pleaded to return to earth, to wrap up all the lose ends in her life. Still in a form and a mind of a child, she returns to their old home, now old and in a state of decay, where she met a cowardly little boy named Andrew. They became best friends as Andrew tries to help Momay find her family.
